WorldStage NewsOnline—-The Nigeria Police Force (NPF),  Bayelsa Command has confirmed the kidnapping of Mr Wellington Magbisa, father of the Chairman of Sagbama Local Government Area of the state by gunmen. DSP Butswat Asinim, Spokesman of the command,made confirmation while addressing newsmen on Sunday in Yenagoa. Asinim said that the kidnappers gained entrance to the victim’s bedroom via an unprotected window and abducted him. “Five men came in through an unprotected window, captured Mr Magbisa and escaped through the waterways,“he said.